{"tid":2376903,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃絲鬧陶傑捧藍絲KOL證明其實香港好多人仲未夠水平睇陶傑","createTime":"2021-01-23T06:58:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-24T06:35:17.000Z","uid":76115,"like":17,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"fa8242b0b693ff18736cbe061862b4c26a48dd0c","tid":2376903,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T06:58:56.000Z","msg":"我自己雖然都係住公屋，ive畢業，但睇咗陶傑十幾年，好多野比你地睇得透好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解陶傑，Andy Koo同埋我呢類精英反民主？最簡單，一個例子，你地民主制講大多數，成日投錯政棍，相反陶傑好多野係睇得前過哂其他人，我地陶迷都知道左膠女權閪大愛撚，就係佢第一個開始批判，而家全部畀佢講中哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（雖然critique of identity politics好似佢出世嗰陣已經有，不過唔好理住當住係先）<br />\n陶傑唔係藍絲，唔係黃絲，佢係一個conservative，一個skeptic，講理性.邏輯.常識，呢類人係永遠喺到思考，永遠喺到探索<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢最鍾意引用羅素嗰句The problem is that fools are so certain of themselves, and <strong>wiser people</strong> so full of doubts，就係我地呢類精英思想者嘅寫照<br />\n陶傑係咩人？好坦白講，你仲問得出呢個問題，就證明你未睇得明陶傑，唔明就出少句聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同一個現代羅素講咩黃藍之見，笑撚死人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb644543afc819eb0136dd7b86b33bcc01097321","tid":2376903,"uid":205928,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T07:00:02.000Z","msg":"又係星期六就出長文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3ed25e347e9884e7214372688db19017c2aaa9b","tid":2376903,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bb644543afc819eb0136dd7b86b33bcc01097321","tid":2376903,"uid":205928,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T07:00:02.000Z","msg":"又係星期六就出長文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T07:04:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fa